column2: SELECT INTO MyDB.photo_lim   L.grpid, SPO.specObjID, SPO.ra, SPO.dec, SPO.z,    SPO.modelMag_u, SPO.modelMag_g, SPO.modelMag_r, SPO.modelMag_i, SPO.modelMag_z FROM MyDB.Lim as L, SpecPhotoAll as SPO OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearbySpecObjEq(MyDB.Lim.ra, MyDB.Lim.dec, MyDB.Lim.aperture) as SO WHERE SPO.specObjID = SO.SpecObjID and SPO.class = &&& and abs(SPO.z - L.zcmb) < # * sqrt(#) * L.sigma
